title: Replay: Bakhtiari, Lacy on Clubhouse Live
text:
Activate your digital access. Replay: Bakhtiari, Lacy on Clubhouse Live Brett Christopherson , Ricardo Arguello , Sarah Riley , Wm. Glasheen , Jim Rosandick , Daniel Damiani and Jordan Schelling , Gannett Wisconsin Media 8:41 p.m. EDT October 5, 2015 Green Bay Packers running Eddie Lacy will be Monday's guest on Clubhouse Live with David Bakhtiari. Watch live at 6:30 p.m. on clubhouselive.com. Or, watch the show in person from The Clubhouse Sports Pub & Grill inside the Radisson Paper Valley Hotel in downtown Appleton. (Photo: Wm. Glasheen/Post-Crescent Media) Live Blog Clubhouse Live with the Packers' Bakhtiari, Lacy  ; 
Green Bay Packers left tackle David Bakhtiari was joined by running back Eddie Lacy on Monday night on Clubhouse Live, Gannett Wisconsin Media's live weekly pro football show Monday from The Clubhouse Sports Pub & Grill in downtown Appleton.
